t proposal to construct time by fixing a\nreference frame. This scheme can be reached both introducing the so-called\n\"kinematical action\", as well as by the well-known Kuchar-Torre formulation. In\nboth cases, the Schr\\\"odinger equation, amended for quantum gravity\ncorrections, has the same morphology and we provide a cosmological\nimplementation of the model, to elucidate its possible predictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2022 17:11:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 18:21:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-27"}
