tify Ce2Zr2O7 as a\nstrong candidate for an octupolar U (1) QSL, establishing that frustrated\nmagnetic octupolar interactions are responsible for QSL properties in Ce-based\npyrochlore magnets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Sep 2022 04:22:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
